sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: Open CreateTaskDialog — load saved drafts
    C->>A: LoadTaskDrafts()
    A->>PM: LoadTaskDrafts()
    PM->>PA: LoadTaskDrafts()
    PA->>PA: ReadFile(tasks/drafts.json)
    PA-->>PM: json.RawMessage
    PM-->>A: json.RawMessage
    A-->>C: string (JSON)
    C->>C: Parse drafts, populate priority quadrants
    C->>C: Migrate legacy string tags to string[]

    Note over C,R: Stage tasks (client-only, no backend calls)
    C->>C: User fills title, theme, description, tags
    C->>C: User clicks "Stage to ⬇" button (1 of 3 quadrants)
    C->>C: Task added to selected priority quadrant
    C->>C: Input fields cleared, title input re-focused

    Note over C,R: Close dialog — persist drafts
    C->>A: SaveTaskDrafts(JSON)
    A->>PM: SaveTaskDrafts(json.RawMessage)
    PM->>PA: SaveTaskDrafts(json.RawMessage)
    PA->>PA: WriteFile(tasks/drafts.json) [no git commit]
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: Commit to Todo — batch create all staged tasks
    C->>C: User clicks "Commit to Todo"
    loop For each task across all priority quadrants
        C->>A: CreateTask(title, themeId, priority, description, tags)
        A->>PM: CreateTask(...)
        PM->>PM: Validate, build task
        PM->>PA: SaveTaskWithOrder(task, dropZone)
        PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
        PM-->>A: *Task
        A-->>C: *Task
        alt CreateTask succeeds
            C->>C: Remove task from pending list
        else CreateTask fails
            C->>C: Keep task in pending list (partial failure)
        end
    end

    alt All tasks created successfully
        C->>A: SaveTaskDrafts("{}") [clear drafts]
        C->>C: Close dialog, trigger EisenKan refresh
    else Partial failure
        C->>C: Show error: "N of M tasks failed to create"
        C->>C: Failed tasks remain staged for retry
    end
